; Default quadcopter (quad X) for GWMultirotorBody. ~0.7 kg 5" quad: 0.13 m arms,
; 5:1 thrust/weight, realistic inertia (auto-estimated). Powerful and agile while
; staying stable on ArduCopter's stock tune. Tune to taste, or assign your own.
